  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">A Moving Lecture Performance</div>
    <h1><span class="typewriter-text" id="hero-tw" data-text="I, Holobiont?"></span></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">A lecture performance combining dance, live sound and biology research — in English, for audiences from 16 to 110.</p>
    <div class="hero-meta">
      Premiere: September 26, 2026 <span>·</span> Vaasa City Library <span>·</span> Janis Heldmann & Nella Turkki
